<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:15:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>台湾表示期待在石破浩领导下深化与日本的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-it-looks-forward-deepening-ties-with-japan-under-ishiba-2024-09-27/</link><description>赖清德领导的民进党周五表示，台湾总统赖清德期待在石破茂领导下深化与日本执政党的关系。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-says-it-looks-forward-deepening-ties-with-japan-under-ishiba-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警称菲律宾船只向仁爱礁运送物资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-says-philippine-vessel-took-supplies-second-thomas-shoal-2024-09-27/</link><description>中国海警周五表示，菲律宾派出一艘民用船向仁爱礁的一艘军舰运送日常必需品，北京称这艘军舰在南海有争议的水道上非法“搁浅”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 08:11:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-coast-guard-says-philippine-vessel-took-supplies-second-thomas-shoal-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国数据公布前，欧洲斯托克 600 指数跌破纪录高位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/stoxx-600-hits-record-high-china-driven-rally-set-weekly-gains-2024-09-27/</link><description>欧洲股市从周五早些时候触及的历史高位回落，因美国重要数据公布前市场普遍谨慎，不过盟可睐 (Moncler) 和奢侈品股的上涨限制了价格的进一步下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 07:37:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/stoxx-600-hits-record-high-china-driven-rally-set-weekly-gains-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>即将领导日本的局外人石破茂是谁？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/shigeru-ishiba-outsider-set-lead-japan-2024-09-27/</link><description>这位 67 岁的领导人在四次尝试失败后终于成功。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 06:39:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/shigeru-ishiba-outsider-set-lead-japan-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国9月份工厂活动继续下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-seen-extending-declines-sept-2024-09-27/</link><description>由于国内需求疲软和全球贸易壁垒不断上升继续困扰着世界第二大经济体，中国的工厂活动可能在 9 月份连续第五个月保持收缩。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 06:21:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-seen-extending-declines-sept-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：上海、深圳取消重点购房限制提振市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-shenzhen-lift-key-home-purchase-curbs-boost-market-sources-say-2024-09-27/</link><description>潜在买家将不再需要接受资格审查，中国其他地方的人们将被允许在热门城市购买房屋。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 06:16:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-shenzhen-lift-key-home-purchase-curbs-boost-market-sources-say-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>美国海岸警卫队观察阿拉斯加附近俄罗斯和中国海军活动的增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-coast-guard-watching-uptick-russian-chinese-navy-activity-near-alaska-2024-09-27/</link><description>一位高级指挥官周五表示，美国海岸警卫队正在观察中国和俄罗斯海军在阿拉斯加和北太平洋周围的活动“增加”，但迄今为止的遭遇都非常专业。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 05:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-coast-guard-watching-uptick-russian-chinese-navy-activity-near-alaska-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国导弹试验后斐济敦促“尊重我们的地区”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/fiji-urges-respect-our-region-after-china-missile-test-2024-09-27/</link><description>在中国发射洲际弹道导弹后，斐济总统拉图·威廉姆·卡托尼韦雷呼吁“尊重我们的地区”并停止在太平洋进行导弹试验。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 04:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/fiji-urges-respect-our-region-after-china-missile-test-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>丰田8月份全球产量连续第7个月下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-global-output-falls-7th-straight-month-august-2024-09-27/</link><description>受日本台风和认证丑闻以及美国两款运动型多用途车产量暂停的拖累，丰田汽车 8 月份全球产量下降 11%，连续第七个月下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 04:38:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-global-output-falls-7th-straight-month-august-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：北京取消政策止损</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-27/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 04:34:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国敦促梅赛德斯-奔驰在汽车领域合作中发挥“积极”作用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-active-role-by-mercedes-benz-auto-sector-co-operation-2024-09-27/</link><description>该机构周五表示，中国国家规划部门负责人在北京会见了梅赛德斯-奔驰管理委员会主席康林松。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 04:01:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-urges-active-role-by-mercedes-benz-auto-sector-co-operation-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市飙升至2008年以来最佳单周，日元因日本领导地位押注而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-27/</link><description>在北京推出大规模刺激计划以重振经济之后，中国股市迎来了自 2008 年以来最好的一周，并帮助亚洲股市升至 2-1/2 年高点，而油价大幅下跌预示着全球通货紧缩的好兆头。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 02:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>资深议员石破浩赢得首相竞选，日元反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-drifts-risk-sensitive-currencies-lifted-by-china-optimism-2024-09-27/</link><description>日本前防卫大臣石破茂赢得日本执政党自民党领导权竞选并有望成为下一任首相后，日元周五反弹，收复早前跌幅。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 01:53:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-drifts-risk-sensitive-currencies-lifted-by-china-optimism-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯周五会见中国外交部长王毅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/blinken-meet-chinese-foreign-minister-wang-yi-friday-2024-09-27/</link><description>美国国务院表示，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯将于周五在纽约会见中国外交部长王毅。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 01:52:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/blinken-meet-chinese-foreign-minister-wang-yi-friday-2024-09-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国工业利润今年遭遇最大降幅，加剧经济困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-industrial-profit-growth-swings-back-decline-august-2024-09-27/</link><description>继 7 月份增长 4.1% 后，8 月份利润同比下降 17.8%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 01:44:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-industrial-profit-growth-swings-back-decline-august-2024-09-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>